message.entry: Specify multiple values as a vector.
Specify region bounds as two vectors of equal length or as a 2-by-n or n-by-2 matrix.
Parent must be a Cartesian axes.
Value must be one of the following: 'numeric' | 'datetime' | 'categorical' | 'duration'
When Values and Labels both contain multiple elements, they must be the same size.
The minimum and maximum values must be scalar.
The minimum and maximum value cannot be empty.
Specify a minimum and maximum value.
Specify region bounds as an n-by-2 matrix of theta spans and an n-by-2 matrix of radius spans.
Specify the plane normals as "x", "y", "z", or as an n-by-3 or 3-by-n numeric matrix.
Specify a single numeric value for the offset or a vector of numeric values.
Plane normals and offsets must be the same length in at least one dimension.
ConstantPlane must be parented to an axes object with numeric rulers.
